#Text=Pörtschach
#Text=Pörtschach am Wörthersee is a city in the Wörthersee region of Carinthia ( Kärnten ) , Austria .
#Text=Get in
#Text=Pörtschach can be easily reached by train .
#Text=Pörtschach has one , right at the centre of the city .
#Text=It has daily connections to Vienna .
#Text=You might also notice that the Austrian train system uses Pörtschach and Pörtschach am Wörthersee interchangeably .
#Text=Get around
#Text=Pörtschach is such a small city that by far the most of it can be reached by foot .
#Text=See
#Text=The views of the local lake , Wörther See , and the Alps beyond are the main sight .
#Text=You can see them from high points , from the banks of the lake and from boats on the lake .
#Text=You can also see many elegant villas that have views of the lake by walking around town .
#Text=Finally , there is a local parish church with stained glass windows .
#Text=Do
#Text=World Bodypainting Festival .
#Text=10 AM to 2 AM .
#Text=The world 's biggest and most famous body painting festival .
#Text=Held on a weekend in early July .
#Text=About a hundred artists and models from all around the world , plus thousands of visitors .
#Text=Provides great opportunities for art photography .
#Text=Also includes live music by various bands , street food and bars .
#Text=55 € for a 3-day pass .
#Text=Lake Wörthersee .
#Text=Go swimming in the lake Wörthersee , right south of the city centre .
#Text=The water is extremely clean and clear , and very warm in the middle of the summer .
#Text=Note that pretty much the entire shore of the lake Wörthersee is private property , because of the dense population of Austria .

#Text=This means that in practice , you have to be a guest of a lakeside hotel ( " Seehotel " in German ) to actually get to the lake shore , and even then you can only visit your own hotel 's property .
#Text=Your hotel will tell you where its share of the lake shore is , and provide you with a key if one is necessary .
#Text=It is advised to bring your own swimming costume and towel .
#Text=The lake itself is public property , so you can swim anywhere you like .
#Text=Just note not to trespass on private properties at the shore .
#Text=When swimming far from the shore , watch out for speedboats , as these are common nearer the centre of the lake .
#Text=Drink
#Text=Café Bar 188 , Hauptstraße 188 , ✉ office@cafe-bar-188.at .
#Text=3 PM to 4 AM in winter , 11 AM to 4 AM in summer .
#Text=A spacious , trendy and comfortable bar right in the middle of the city .
#Text=Also functions as pretty much the only night club in Pörtschach .
#Text=Has a spacious terrace .
#Text=Hosts various events almost all year round .
#Text=Beer about 3.30 € .
#Text=Schwarze Luft , Hauptstraße 177 , ☏ +436643418656 .
#Text=A small , no-frills pub located right in the centre of Pörtschach .
#Text=One of the very few establishments in Pörtschach to stay open after midnight .
#Text=Good choices in beer and other drinks , but food only comes in the way of snacks .
#Text=Beer 3.70 € .
#Text=Sleep
#Text=Ambassador , Moosburger Straße 51 , ☏ +43-660-4215208 , ✉ gottfried.samitz@aon.at .
#Text=A large and comfortable hotel in central Pörtschach , but a bit far away from the lake shore .
#Text=Note that to get to the hotel , you have to walk through thick columns of trees and bushes .
#Text=Rooms starting from 62 € / night .
#Text=Hotel Balance , Winklernerstraße 68 , ☏ +4342722479 , ✉ office@balancehotel.at .
#Text=A luxurious hotel concentrating on the well-being of the mind and the body .
#Text=Various opportunities for relaxation , exercise and treatment available on-site .
#Text=The rooms are very spacious and stylishly decorated .
#Text=Of course , the prices reflect this .
#Text=Prices are given per person - double rooms starting from 176 € ( 88 € / person ) .
#Text=Werzer 's Hotels am Wörthersee , Werzerpromenade 8 , Pörtschach Austria , ☏ +43 4272-22310 .
#Text=4-star spa resorts in three different parts of the Wörthersee : Pörtschach , Techelsberg and Velden .
